## 消息处理模块

### 1. 流式聊天接口(故事)

- **URL**: `/chat/completions/story/{story_id}/{message_id}`
- **Method**: POST
- **Request Body**:

  ```json
  {
    "message_content": "你好！",
  }
  ```

- **Response**: (SSE流式响应)

  ```json
  {"type": "init", "user_message_id": "msg_123", "ai_message_id": "msg_456", "done":false}
  ```

  ```json
  {"type": "message", "id": "msg_456", "value": "你好！", "done": false}
  ```

  ```json
  {"type": "message", "id": "msg_456", "value": "有什么可以帮助你的？", "done": true}
  ```

### 2. 流式聊天接口(对话)

- **URL**: `/chat/completions/conversation/{story_id}/{message_id}`
- **Method**: POST
- **Request Body**:

  ```json
  {
    "message_content": "你好",
  }
  ```

- **Response**: (SSE流式响应)

  同上

